    Question SN303("Stimularea parasimpatica produce asupra vaselor sanguine :\n\n A. In principal vasoconstrictie \n B. Dilatalie in toate teritoriile vasculare \n C. Dilatatie in cateva teritorii vasculare \n D. Vasoconstrictie in toate teritoriile vasculare \n E. Vasoconstrictie in muschii scheletici ", "C", 303);
